cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use genoselect, please cite it as below."
title: "genoselect: scikit-learn-compatible genomic prediction and selection"
abstract: >-
  A Python toolkit for genomic prediction from SNP marker data: the VanRaden
  genomic relationship matrix, GBLUP by REML, machine-learning predictors, a
  stacked super-learner ensemble, and breeding-relevant cross-validation, all as
  scikit-learn-compatible estimators.
type: software
authors:
